snippet.textDisplay:
Astaghfaar .....Nabi paak SAW is dunya mai hummai yai tableeq kernai ayai thay Kai hum Allah paak kai saath kissi ko shareek naa karai Allah kai ilawa kisii sai madad naa maangai...aur ajj Kal kai musalmaan Allah paak kai ilawa kisi aur sai khaw wo NABI ho Ya wali ho Ya koi aur unsai unhai pukaar rahai hain unsai madad maang rahai hain unkai tableeq kai bilkul khilaaf karrahi hain..jo Kai saaf shirk hai jiski maufi bhi nhi hai.......
.Mushkil kusha,, madad gaar,, hamiyai bekasa Srif aur Srif Allah paak hain jholi srif Allah paak hi bherta hai..intezamaat Allah hi kerta hai aur Allah paak hi ilm gaib jaanta hai  .
Ghor karain..hum musalmaan Nabi SAW sai pyaar kernai ka dawa kertai hain. Tab hi shaytaan  kuch nadaan musalmano sai Nabi PAAK ka naam leker shirk kerwa raha hai . Jis gunah ki maaufi bhi nahi hai 
.socho jab NAbi SAW ko qiyamat mai pata chalaiga kai yai log mujhai Allah kai saath shareek kertai thay tab unhai kitna duk hoga
